window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Jebediah Trapper is a ticking time bomb.</b></p> <p>After sort of saving the day months ago, he's got a nuclear bomb attached to him in the Fate Dimension, where magic and potential collide.</p> <p>Jeb just wants to defuse himself before he collapses into a sickly pile of green goo or ignites in a city-destroying blast.</p> <p>There's just one problem: The world doesn't slow down because you've got a nuclear hangnail. Mab, Queen of the Fae wants him for unknown, yet most likely sinister reasons. A mysterious, abhorrent entity is making him an offer he can't refuse, and the undead are getting organized.</p> <p>The bomb can wait...right?</p>"; 
